    Name=A;
      IsoId=O75330-1; Sequence=Displayed;
    Name=B;
      IsoId=O75330-2; Sequence=VSP_004286;
-!- TISSUE SPECIFICITY: Expressed in breast cancer cell lines and in
    normal breast tissue.
